0Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢點追你（如果唔係追就講下點一齊啦）</blockquote><br />\n我成日都笑佢無追我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識左幾日已經覺得大家好夾 <br />\n由朝到晚都會wtsapp，個陣已經覺得會一齊<br />\n但我覺得我地係兩個世界既人<br />\n佢話 同你同齡既男仔除左出世早過我之外 有咩佢地有 而我冇😂 我覺得兩個世界係指大家價值觀唔同先會係兩個唔同既世界<br />\n<br />\n咁佢又講得岩 同埋佢份人唔似細過我，有夢想有計劃。<br />\n之後有次係公園我話我同佢星座真係好夾 <br />\n（個陣大家已經想一齊，星座依個話題之前有講開。）<br />\n佢話 咁夾不如一齊，我就應承左佢😂"},{"pid":"ef9dd143dd44f48ea0fb6e07c6801a588f143a4d","tid":238910,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:43:43.000Z","msg":"女朋友大我2年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e26b1f582bc14d97a84e26fc81c5e90fa923c1","tid":238910,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:45:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點識？</blockquote><br />\n做gym識</blockquote><br />\n邊個主動先？"},{"pid":"f9fa8cc09dacc6dff915053755b74b0865b514fb","tid":238910,"uid":111412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:46:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女方會唔會覺得有時男方比自己思想同處理事情上表現得比較細個同幼稚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nUm 都有架，因為我經歷過既野多過佢<br />\n我岩岩同佢一齊既時候，我地去行玩具反斗城<br />\n我個陣覺得佢拎個面具玩好幼稚😂<br />\n我到而家都唔明點解我會咁諗<br />\n佢個陣feel到我唔鍾意佢就無再做過<br />\n之後講返我而家又唔係好介意<br />\n<br />\n不過我覺得佢已經比好同佢同齡既人成熟，個陣佢想同我玩先咁做既姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e410205c5fa1e82ceda31ba2ad891e7bfa7d984","tid":238910,"uid":111412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:48:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同男朋友用同一個ac<br />\n我大佢三年，一齊左就黎一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左我去旅行既日子之外 keep住日日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哋冇嘢做嘅咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我返工佢返學呀<br />\n我地屋企係隔黎個座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果佢dayoff就會係樓下接我收工<br />\n返學如果返早就會一齊返"},{"pid":"12b653674921d04fb5d072f8fdc83d6f81c8b514","tid":238910,"uid":111412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:49:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點識？</blockquote><br />\n做gym識</blockquote><br />\n邊個主動先？</blockquote><br />\n男呀 佢話個日佢留意左我好耐<br />\n話好少見女仔認真做gym 話想識個朋友一齊做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549efca06c8c6d3ae06faafa5b668debce68bdb5","tid":238910,"uid":111412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:50:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我25 女友29 黎緊結婚</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 恭喜你呀 你地幾多歲一齊呀"},{"pid":"49421a2f4b45d02a07a1d887f0a48d45167cf4fa","tid":238910,"uid":111412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女朋友大我2年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你地幾多歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56ec4ea917cf48b5d607e8a3a2326db608f1979","tid":238910,"uid":111412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:51:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>追緊個一樣大我三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMore <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ace4a5f27494fc671ba23fd6f83735d83a613a4","tid":238910,"uid":111412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女方大4年，拍左差唔多2年，準備求婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恭喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img